<%- include ../partials/header.ejs %>
<%- include ../partials/top_nav.ejs %>
 
<main class="container">
    <br>
    <h3>Current Projects</h3>
    <a href="/projects/add" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus fa-lg"></i> Add Project</a>
    <br>
    <table class="table table-striped table-hover">
        <thead>
            <tr>
              <th scope="col">Title</th>
              <th scope="col">Loan</th>
              <th scope="col">Description</th>
              <th scope="col">Deadline</th>
              <th scope="col">Update</th>
              <th scope="col">Delete</th>
              
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% for (let index = 0; index < ProjectList.length; index++) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= ProjectList[index].pname %></td>
                    <td><%= ProjectList[index].loanApplied ? 'Loan Applied' : 'Loan Not Applied' %></td>
                    <td><%= ProjectList[index].pdescription %></td>
                    <td><%= new Date(ProjectList[index].pdeadline).toLocaleString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric'}) %></td>
                    <td>
                      <a href="/projects/edit/<%= ProjectList[index].id %>" class="btn btn-info btn-sm"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-pen fa-lg"></i> Update</a>
                    </td>

                    <td>
                      <a href="/projects/delete/<%= ProjectList[index].id %>" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onClick="return confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this project?')"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash fa-lg"></i> Delete</a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            <% } %>
          </tbody>
    </table>

      <h3>Previous Projects</h3>
  
      <!-- Project 1 -->
      <div class="project">
          <h4>Project 1: Photo Viewer</h4>
          <p>This project entailed modifying an existing application to add more user-friendly features and enhance the user interface. The project is built using Node.js and Express.</p>
          <img src="/images/project1_screenshot.jpg" alt="Project 1 Screenshot">
          <p>Key features include:</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Adding a picture to a favorite area.</li>
              <li>Limiting favorites to a maximum of 5.</li>
              <li>Option to remove favorites.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/Chuileee/express-generator-app/tree/master/project/project1" class="project-link">View Project 1</a>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Project 2 -->
      <div class="project">
          <h4>Project 2: Bug Smasher Game</h4>
          <p>This project involved implementing a simple browser-based game. The game features a bug hopping randomly around the game area. The player tries to catch the bug by clicking on it. This project is built using HTML5 and JavaScript.</p>
          <img src="/images/project2_screenshot.jpg" alt="Project 2 Screenshot">
          <p>Key features include:</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Increasing score when the bug is smashed.</li>
              <li>Decreasing the hopping interval when the bug is smashed.</li>
              <li>Option to reset the game speed.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/Chuileee/express-generator-app/tree/master/project/project2" class="project-link">View Project 2</a>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Project 3 -->
      <div class="project">
          <h4>Project 3: Image Gallery</h4>
          <p>This project involved implementing a simple Image gallery using Ajax and jQuery. It displays pictures specified in a file, with user navigation controls. This project is built using jQuery and AJAX for seamless user experience.</p>
          <img src="/images/project3_screenshot.jpg" alt="Project 3 Screenshot">
          <p>Key features include:</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Previous and Next navigation buttons.</li>
              <li>Update button to reload the picture list from the file.</li>
              <li>Smooth transitions between pictures using jQuery animations.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/Chuileee/express-generator-app/tree/master/project/project3" class="project-link">View Project 3</a>
      </div>
      

</main>

